overview: Rich Cronin, Brad Fischetti and Devin Lima offer their unique blend of pop, hip-hop and R&B on this special video that includes interview footage, a live performance in Orlando, Fla., a rare behind-the-scenes look at a band photo shoot and three exciting music videos. LFO performs many of their best-loved hits, including "Summer Girls," "Girl on TV," "I Don't Wanna Kiss You Goodnight" and "West Side Story."
title: LFO: Live from Orlando & More
